  "detailed_description": "<strong>It's in the name, <i>Easy</i>. The easiest to use VTT, and we mean it.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grid System</strong></h2>Unique and <i>Easy</i> scaling grid system -- scale your map to any grid size! <br>The grid scales to a maximum of 120x120 for 14,400 tiles.<br>Upload your custom maps or any images of your choice. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606600/extras/534534981ef98403d4eec4aa96bf4918.poster.avif?t=1731101550\" width=480 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606600/extras/534534981ef98403d4eec4aa96bf4918.webm?t=1731101550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606600/extras/534534981ef98403d4eec4aa96bf4918.mp4?t=1731101550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fog of War</strong></h2><i>Easy</i> to apply, drag and drop, Fog of War system. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606600/extras/7a12a52dac4af098dd3808df41a11388.poster.avif?t=1731101550\" width=480 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606600/extras/7a12a52dac4af098dd3808df41a11388.webm?t=1731101550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606600/extras/7a12a52dac4af098dd3808df41a11388.mp4?t=1731101550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Selection</strong></h2>Drag box selection with copy and paste! <br>Select multiple tokens, adjust color, size, images, rotation, and much more. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606600/extras/a865f9de239760b30fde3f99887cfd59.poster.avif?t=1731101550\" width=480 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606600/extras/a865f9de239760b30fde3f99887cfd59.webm?t=1731101550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606600/extras/a865f9de239760b30fde3f99887cfd59.mp4?t=1731101550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Saving</strong></h2>Upload your entire collection of 2D tokens into a 3D world!  <br>Save and Load your tables, including tokens and FX, at the click of a button! <br>The file system supports map images up to 100MB in file size.<br><br>Setting up your table has never been so <i><strong>Easy</strong></i>!<br><br><i>Note: Players must own the game to join tables.</i>",
